data.description: Beautiful 3 bedroom 2 bathroom home located in Ranches East subdivision. Home has new paint, granite in kitchen and split bedrooms. Great starter home for first time buyers. Home is right across the street from the community pool and neighborhood has a lot to offer! Home wont last long!
